Encrypt:
	cryptsetup luksFormat /dev/xxx

Open:
	cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/xxx yyy

Mount:
	mount -t ext4 /dev/mapper/yyy /mnt

Close:
	cryptsetup luksClose yyy

Reencrypt:
	cryptsetup reencrypt /dev/xxx

Add pass:
	cryptsetup luksAddKey /dev/xxx

Rm pass:
	cryptsetup luksRemoveKey /dev/xxx

See how many pass:
	cryptsetup luksDump /dev/xxx

Test pass:
	cryptsetup open --verbose --test-passphrase /dev/xxx
